videos.headline: Florida recovers fumble
videos.description: Tennessee QB Jarrett Guarantano is leveled by Florida's Jachai Polite and the ball falls in the hands of David Reese II.

videos.headline: Florida FB gets easy TD
videos.description: Florida fullback R.J. Raymond gets his first career catch and it is a 1-yard TD score.

videos.headline: Franks lowers shoulder for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Florida QB Feleipe Franks powers it in for his first career rushing TD giving the Gators 14 points off turnovers.

videos.headline: Florida stuffs the RB for a safety
videos.description: Tennessee RB Tim Jordan is swarmed in the end zone for a Florida safety.

videos.headline: Florida extends lead with 65-yard touchdown
videos.description: Florida QB Feleipe Franks rolls right and finds Freddie Swain downfield for the 65-yard TD.

videos.headline: Tennessee fumbles away easy TD
videos.description: Austin Pope is running for the easy touchdown but is stripped and the ball goes through the end zone for the touchback.

videos.headline: Scarlett breaks tackles and scores Florida TD
videos.description: Florida RB Jordan Scarlett breaks multiple tackles and powers in for the 19-yard rushing TD.

videos.headline: Florida WR goes up and grabs the ball for TD
videos.description: Florida WR Tyrie Cleveland goes up and snags the ball for the 38-yard TD.

videos.headline: Banks fights his way for Tennessee TD
videos.description: Tennessee RB Jeremy Banks powers his way into the end zone for the 2-yard TD run.

videos.headline: Florida RB scores the easy 24-yard score
videos.description: Florida RB Dameon Pierce breaks free for the easy 47-yard TD run.
